name: Find Woman
description:
Your wife(s) got lost under some red cups, pick them up but dont pick up the one cup without your wife. 

If u play thing i guess u can make it more fun by doing stuff u litterly just click stuff u can make a mini dungeon or draw some art. It is litterly a joke that was meant to be made in 6 hours but the idea transformed so much that it took 36 hours.
